race.comment: INNERVISIONS (8) returned in fine fashion with a dominant Beaudesert victory and winning rider Moor sticks in the stirrups. Drawn to get across easily from gate four and should give backers a bold sight. MOTORBIKE (13) is one from one around this circuit and will be ready to peak now fourth run back from a break. Shapes as a leading contender. LIMAHULI (1) strips fitter second-up from the break and gets the services of Mallyon in the saddle. In the mix. ORIENTE (2) got up to Group 2 level when last in work and strips fitter third-up from the break. Shapes as one to consider. BRAVE JET (16) next best from the low draw.
